
@{
    Layout = null;
}

<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>常见问题</title>
    <style>
        .addinfo {
            width: auto;
            height: 180px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body ontouchstart style="background-color:#f8f8f8">
    <div class="weui-cells__title" style="font-weight:bolder;">奖金系统如何管理员工?</div>
    <div> 
        <p>1.通过点击底部导航栏的【功能】按钮,进入功能界面->点击【员工管理】->通过点击同步图片进行同步员工操作;点击部门后查看此部门中对应的员工（注：此操作同步您企业通讯录里的员工，当企业通讯录发生变化时，请点击同步按钮，让数据一致）</p>
        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-around;">
            <img src="~/Content/Images/faq/user/员工.png" class="addinfo" />
            <img src="~/Content/Images/faq/user/add.png" class="addinfo" />
            @*<img src="~/Content/Images/faq/user/addinfo.png" class="addinfo" />*@
       </div>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p>2.同步员工成功后通过点击【编辑员工】页面，左滑有编辑员工(注：姓名、联系电话、电子邮箱不能更改，如需更改，请到您微信后台更改)</p>
        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-around;">
            <img src="~/Content/Images/faq/user/left1.png" class="addinfo"/>
            <img src="~/Content/Images/faq/user/left2.png" class="addinfo"/>
            <img src="~/Content/Images/faq/user/edituser.png" class="addinfo"/>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p>3.部门与上述员工一致，同步完成后给部门相关负责人即可。</p>
        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-around;">
            <img src="~/Content/Images/faq/user/depleft1.png" class="addinfo" />
            <img src="~/Content/Images/faq/user/depleft2.png" class="addinfo" />
            <img src="~/Content/Images/faq/user/depleft3.png" class="addinfo" />
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
